Package: enigma2-plugin-extensions-fbc-channelspeedchange
Version: 0.3.2
Architecture: all
Maintainer: empyfi <empyfi@users.noreply.github.com>
Section: extensions
Priority: optional
Depends: enigma2
Description: FBC-accelerated channel zapping for OpenATV
 Pre-tunes next, previous, and history channels on free FBC demodulators
 so that channel switches complete in milliseconds. Recording and PiP
 always take precedence; the pre-tune pool releases demodulators on demand
 and re-arms automatically afterwards.
Homepage: https://github.com/empyfi/FBC-ChannelSpeedChange
